To reproduce the prog. mom. flux results, go to the top directory and issue
the following commands:

./compile/compile.bash

./run_scripts/run_scm.bash <casename> --netcdf

where <casename> denotes either bomex or dycoms2_rf02_do.

To reproduce the eddy diffusivity results, replace the file

input/tunable_parameters/configurable_model_flags.in

with

input/tunable_parameters/configurable_model_flags.in.diagmom

and then simply re-run the case.

To create plots, go to postprocessing/python_sam_budgets_plotter and type:

python plotgen_main.py

To plot SAM fields, SAM output will be required.

